*Razmislite* o svojim ciljevima u životu (Think about your goals in life).

*Razmišljajući* o njenom izboru, shvatili smo da je bila tačna (Thinking about her choice, we realized it was correct).

Moramo *razmisliti* o dobrom načinu da rešimo taj problem (We have to think about a good way to solve that problem).

*Razmišljala* je o svojoj budućnosti (She was thinking about her future).

Mnogo je razmišljalo o tome da li je to bila dobra odluka (Many have been thinking about whether that was a good decision).